  <summary>Audio Effects for Pulseaudio Applications</summary>
  <developer_name>Wellington Wallace</developer_name>
  <description>
    <p>
      PulseEffects is an advanced audio manipulation tool with multiple features.
      It is an equalizer, limiter, reverb and compressor and it has automatic volume
      effects. Additionally, because PulseEffects uses the PulseAudio sound server
      it will support nearly all apps available, i.e web browser, media player, etc.
    </p>
    <p>
      Besides working with applications it is possible to simultaneously apply effects
      to a microphone's output.
    </p>
    <p>
      PulseEffects will conveniently remember all of the settings from your last
      session. Multiple configurations can be saved by using profiles.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Automatic Volume Control</li>
      <li>Compressor</li>
      <li>Equalizer</li>
      <li>Input Limiter</li>
      <li>Profiles</li>
      <li>Reverberation</li>
      <li>Signal Tester</li>
      <li>Spectrum Visualizer</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
